name: Happy Halloween 2021
description:
It's that time of the year again.  Halloween candy! Pokemon like to go trick-or-treating too! In honor of this spooky holiday, I did a watercolor of Pikachu and his pals on their journey to get as many Rare Candies as they can before the night ends!

Hope you all have a safe and happy Halloween.  Whether you're going trick-or-treating with your kids or partying with your friends.  Stay safe.  Stay happy.  Eat some candy!
